  "id": "RAW_b95c2472",
  "title": "一手实测豆包手机助手，这就是当今手机 Agent 的天花板。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647677318&idx=1&sn=5144389b51ae7d3624ff27ab67d94c71",
  "date": "2025-12-01 05:29:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就在刚刚，豆包的手机助手，终于发布了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500193657\" data-ratio=\"0.600925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d21cbf68&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrqZQd9dtnc2HAnQ7vEYnc0hx0eV0qFuxshOLBRZWEoLiaIcrduq784aWMZ9f9Xk3SqBCeliboU63lQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">快憋死我了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-indent: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上周其实豆包的朋友，就跟我说说有个很有意思的新东西，想不想测试一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我说那必须要啊。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">她就神奇的问我：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500193620\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.32456140350877194\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"228\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"228\" data-backh=\"74\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40b859c1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqkHFLqp4Z2zMWLozXJOJUBeLt49f36cFQYEfFy3jE191Zx1zAeE9MfTjcIVz7bvJ2kHYVCBOFSTQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后我就拿到了一台个非常有趣的东西，豆包手机助手，不过还是技术预览版。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">载体是一个跟中兴合作的工程样机。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500193664\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c47752ac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURrqZQd9dtnc2HAnQ7vEYnc0EZWDLrNCricXJ0INU9ibSWUicfrreibN8TbibicjmUdMU00q9PQd772I1ZAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">为了让我们体验豆包手机助手，直接现搓的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我当场献上我的膝盖。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在拿到以后，我就，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">把我的备用机上的所有的数据和微信都移过去了，在深度使用一周，我想说，这玩意，真的没有辜负我的预期。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">这就是一个，基于大模型能力的，真正的AI手机助手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">苹果的apple intelligence还是个饼，但豆包真正意义上的先来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">十几年前乔布斯心中的siri，在这一刻，我觉得才真正的具象化了出来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先给大家看看，这个豆包手机助手，在手机里，能干出什么花活。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如，下载手游的时候，它不仅能够帮我下完游戏，还能把游戏内部的安装包也一并给我下了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像这样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">视频我快放了一下，整个过程大概花了七八分钟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我为了演示，给你们录了下载的全过程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但实际用的时候，豆包手机助手，就一个超级牛逼的一点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是它每一次执行任务，全部是后台运行的，不会抢占你的手机操作界面，运行状态是吸附在顶部的灵动岛里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500193627\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15615141955835962\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"634\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cffe337a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqkHFLqp4Z2zMWLozXJOJUB2KRsSMyTNX9micphIXibJld3bKS9qiaOVeeGxHKWGGjlpkpPtOQaEH0gg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也就是说，这七八分钟里你完全可以继续刷手机，它就在后台下载，你俩井水不犯河水，不用再当心游戏下安装包的时候需要一直在那挂着等它下完了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整个过程中我只在用户协议与隐私政策那里手动点了一下，这种信息肯定还是得自己确认。但其他的，我一点都没动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就，真的很省事儿。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也可以随口和豆包说一句话，让它帮你找个歌单放歌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更好玩的是，我发现它居然还能进小程序里玩小游戏，比如玩合成大西瓜，虽然说玩的让人看着有点脑溢血，但是确实能玩起来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还能跨APP，做各种复杂的操作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 1 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如，拿我自己的一个高频场景打车来举例。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然，在知道目的地的情况下，自己打开滴滴叫车是最方便的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是我大部分的场景都是，不知道目的地。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">经常是有人几天前和我约好了个什么事儿的时候，给我发了一个定位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"209\" data-backw=\"502\" data-imgfileid=\"500193622\" data-ratio=\"0.4163346613545817\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"502\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c3374c55&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqkHFLqp4Z2zMWLozXJOJUB4AunCiabThiaic1l0Dl2ogY9Kq1Rvrl0xjEkVY9aZNFLLvJeO03Ft6m4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">几天后我要出发了，去聊天记录里kuku一通翻，再把这个定位输入到打车软件里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很麻烦。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但我现在就可以直接跟豆包说，前几天我和谁谁约在哪个地方来着？帮我打开微信看一眼，然后给我打个车。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点进豆包就能看到它正在一步步执行，先是打开微信，然后找到聊天记录里的地址，再然后打开滴滴，把地址粘在终点一栏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">到了我这儿，需要的就只是付款了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这，就是豆包深度集成进手机系统以后的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在我这几天测试下来，任务成功率高到离谱，只要你把你的需求表达准确，成功率基本都在80%以上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是我用了一圈安卓手机以后，操作手机能力最牛逼的，没有之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说真的，毕竟是豆包，在模型能力上，特别是在图形界面操作能力上，真的强的离谱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说说豆包手机助手怎么用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">首先，因为现在各大厂家的限制，几乎没有办法用rom包刷机了，而且这种级别的手机助手，也不是一个普普通通的APK安装包能搞定的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，豆包也悄悄上架了他们跟中兴合作的一个手机，主要就是为了让大家体验到豆包手机助手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">感兴趣的朋友，可以去豆包手机助手的官网：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://o.doubao.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://o.doubao.com/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500193665\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5888446215139442\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1255\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0df96842&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURrqZQd9dtnc2HAnQ7vEYnc0aaC1K6VDoOdGEqbe1XHfXnJyicoKsgZPEygR6JicvdF3oX1WibEw4krww%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我其实非常希望各大手机厂商，能跟豆包合作，把豆包手机助手接进去，说实话，这种Agent能力，还是得AI厂商自己干才行。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当你拿到手机之后。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在系统-设置里找到豆包智能，然后点击开启豆包助手，就OK了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500193577\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0092592592592593\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4142\" data-height=\"4181\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a0db607f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURqkHFLqp4Z2zMWLozXJOJUBZaLFu8ia1D5DXSthTfIziaKGmUV4qm8YzIwWsan3gs9Y8dYUKorPzbaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，你就可以正常在屏幕上打开豆包。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">或者用手机上定制的AI键直接打开。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个时候，你就会发现底部最左边多了一个操作手机的按钮，这就说明，你的豆包手机助手已经打开了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500193666\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5142405063291139\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1264\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 297px;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/OjgKEXmLURrqZQd9dtnc2HAnQ7vEYnc0fqUqcXYibtBAFKPoVGfYB8FyzKYibnZvnQR8uPozVKLe25qCWSzjHMGQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1264.0000000000002\" data-cropy1=\"2110.311418685121\" data-cropy2=\"2759.8062283737027\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=31da264e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURrqZQd9dtnc2HAnQ7vEYnc08lZguUPaJnGPefFFgBpzqViakFGbg6Ywnib6bJDG7trDYlDwgCUmL7LQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你可以直接文字输入你的需求，也可以语音对话。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;